### Create Product API [POST]
It creates a product

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "name": "XBox",
            "price": 70000,
            "provider": "Microsoft",
            "rating": 3.5,
            "status": "sale"
        }

+ Request (application/x-www-form-urlencoded)

        name=XBox&price=70000&provider=Microsoft&rating=3.5&status=sale

